block.comment: Repeatedly use the camera to generate costumes for object detection. This requests the faster but less accurate version report at most 10 objects so long as their confidence score is at least 0.25. The defaults, if not provided, are slower and more accurate, at most 20 objects reported, and 0.5 confidence minimum.
